{"tid":2495916,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"溫家寶：我心目中的中國應該是一個『充滿公平正義的國家』","createTime":"2021-04-19T13:00:21.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-19T17:55:25.000Z","uid":293677,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"484dda37439ec9932e960bf94e15c85c139c373a","tid":2495916,"uid":293677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T13:00:21.000Z","msg":"2021/04/19 05:30<br />\n<br />\n〔國際新聞中心／綜合報導〕前中國國務院總理溫家寶的母親去年十二月逝世，溫家寶為紀念亡母，今年三月二十五日至四月十五日在「澳門導報」發表四篇題為「我的母親」的文章。前三篇文章皆有被「微信」與「鳳凰網」等媒體轉載，<span class=\"red\">但第四篇卻疑似因提及「我心目中的中國，應該是一個充滿公平正義的國家」，據傳「微信」上雖然還能看到這篇文章，但已被禁止分享，鳳凰網的轉載內容也遭刪除。</span><br />\n<br />\n微信上禁止分享<br />\n<br />\n溫家寶撰寫的前三篇文章旨在追憶母親的一生。引起爭議的第四篇，則是抒發自身在中共官場的心情，並引述母親在他擔任總理期間，寫給他的兩封信。溫家寶在信末發表感言，表示<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"x-large\">「我同情窮人、同情弱者，反對欺侮和壓迫。我心目中的中國應該是一個『充滿公平正義的國家』，那裡永遠有對人心、人道和人的本質的尊重，永遠有青春、自由、奮鬥的氣質」</span></span>。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">對於溫家寶的憶母文被禁止分享且被媒體刪除，不少中國網友感嘆，連曾貴為國家領導人的溫家寶都受這般對待，其他人遭遇可想而知。</span>中國獨立媒體人高瑜更指出，溫家寶的「四個意識」（政治意識、大局意識、核心意識、看齊意識）、「兩個維護」（維護習近平黨中央的核心、全黨的核心地位，維護黨中央權威和集中統一領導）的自覺性與領悟性，無論如何都比（騰訊及微信創辦人）馬化騰的水準更高，「微信」居然連溫在清明紀念母親的文章都封鎖，令人無語。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/paper/1443917\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fpaper%2F1443917&d=CDYmK9DOGPUFxvwNhHfqxxT9vY2lxR77dvs0GIZdErU%3D&h=f225013a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fpaper%2F1443917&h=aa4680a0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/paper/1443917</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/arrogant.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span class=\"limegreen\">即使係前国家領導人都無言論自由</span>"},{"pid":"8b2ea99c7822fefd0c7115ecb68421a2150cad07","tid":2495916,"uid":293677,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T13:01:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n影帝都無面俾"},{"pid":"3f547845b724a7a5eba209a981715413dd93c688","tid":2495916,"uid":166729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T13:02:24.000Z","msg":"有冇原文留底?"},{"pid":"8a7169de565b3c9630507e718e376876c814280e","tid":2495916,"uid":346701,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T13:02:58.000Z","msg":"禁評<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf4f5392b1938ce0f7514740f6ab757f6925fb9e","tid":2495916,"uid":289946,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T13:05:51.000Z","msg":"咁公平正義佢做唔到平保大股東啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6515059aadf72c0ad2360698d1f94f4bfe353b1","tid":2495916,"uid":44209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T13:08:20.000Z","msg":"主的靈在我身上，因為他用膏膏我，叫我傳福音給貧窮的人，差遣我報告被擄的得釋放、瞎眼的得看見，叫那受壓制的得自由，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9808dbaee7e535f0ec61728297d3d1f807b5a5fc","tid":2495916,"uid":224066,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T13:10:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmRvGYThBgUh3XpVjfSinz8pDQH59a5DcRmacqfKCM8QrS?filename=k9ZRWru.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fk9ZRWru.jpg&h=8104d8c5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e488af215603c5ee779fa47711ced83eac847a9d","tid":2495916,"uid":198035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T17:55:25.000Z","msg":"lm"}]}